ðŸ“Œ Task

Create a React component named OtpInput that collects a 6-digit numeric OTP from the user.

âœ… Requirements

1. UI Requirements

Display 6 input boxes in a single horizontal row.

Each input box should accept only one digit (0â€“9).

If the user types a non-digit, ignore it.

2. Behavior Requirements

When a user types a digit, the focus should automatically move to the next box.

When the user presses Backspace on an empty box, focus should move to the previous box.

3. Completion Requirements

When all 6 boxes are filled, the component should call a function:

onComplete(otpString)

where otpString is like "928371".
